content.raw:
I see where you're coming from. It's weird to have models without plugins. This should really go in the non-existent PropShop (which presumably allows you to distribute plugins with the models).

I'm ok with just dropping this in favor of either waiting for a propshop to happen, or just continuing to distribute things ourselves.
